140 U.S. 183

11 S.Ct. 727

35 L.Ed. 385

CLUETT et al.
v.
McNEANY et al.

May 11, 1891.

Saml. A. Duncan and James A. Skilton, for appellants.

David Tim, for appellees.

PER CURIAM.

1

As this case also turns upon the validity of the same patent, (Cluett v. Claflin, ante, 725,) the decree of the court below is affirmed.
